Wonderful. Now, act cute.

268
00:28:34,220 --> 00:28:35,476
That's it. Thank you.

269
00:28:35,500 --> 00:28:37,260
So cute. Congratulations again.

270
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:39,380
- See you at the party.
- Okay.

271
00:28:42,800 --> 00:28:43,900
Hello.

272
00:28:44,180 --> 00:28:45,476
Mum!

273
00:28:45,500 --> 00:28:46,236
Thank you.

274
00:28:46,260 --> 00:28:47,197
Please be careful.

275
00:28:47,221 --> 00:28:48,780
Hello.

276
00:28:50,220 --> 00:28:51,220
Careful, Mum.

277
00:28:52,730 --> 00:28:54,130
Wow, You're so beautiful.

278
00:28:55,800 --> 00:28:56,600
Hello.

279
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:57,700
Hello.

280
