because you didn't do anything wrong.

286
00:29:16,420 --> 00:29:20,060
After this, I hope you'll
enjoy life without any worries.

287
00:29:24,540 --> 00:29:25,540
Yes.

288
00:29:27,100 --> 00:29:28,100
Nam.

289
00:29:31,930 --> 00:29:36,740
From now on, I'll leave her in your care.

290
00:29:39,060 --> 00:29:43,540
Please don't worry. I'll
never let go of her hand.

291
00:29:44,160 --> 00:29:47,660
I promise I'll love and cherish
her for the rest of my life.

292
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:51,980
