301
00:30:11,760 --> 00:30:13,360
I need to start work first, okay?

302
00:30:25,760 --> 00:30:27,360
Who are you looking for?

303
00:30:29,500 --> 00:30:32,060
I'm looking for Din and Rose.

304
00:30:32,800 --> 00:30:34,260
Lom and Fai too.

305
00:30:35,300 --> 00:30:37,540
The ceremony is about to
begin but they're not here yet.

306
00:30:48,900 --> 00:30:49,900
Wat.

307
00:30:50,530 --> 00:30:51,530
Hello.

308
00:30:52,860 --> 00:30:53,860
Congratulations.

309
00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:23,900
And now, it's time we
all have been waiting for.

310
00:31:28,460 --> 00:31:31,980
I'm so happy for them! Sorry, Boss.

311
00:31:33,380 --> 00:31:39,540
Please give a deafening applause to
our beloved groom and bride for tonight-.

312
00:31:40,580 --> 00:31:48,580
Miss Apo Watinwanich and her
beautiful bride, Miss Chonlada Kunanon!

313
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:35,836
Thank you everyone for such
a warm and loud welcome.

314
00:32:35,860 --> 00:32:40,980
Without the wedding sign, I think people
could've easily mistaken it as a concert.

315
00:32:45,260 --> 00:32:46,860
I'm so nervous right now.

316
00:32:47,460 --> 00:32:52,500
It is our utmost pleasure to have
you with us here at our wedding.

317
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:56,780
Honestly, I never imagined
I'd be standing right here.

318
00:32:58,600 --> 00:33:02,500
My first priority in life
has always been work.

319
00:33:06,660 --> 00:33:14,660
I was so consumed that my friends and family were
pretty sure I'd end up marrying work one day.

320
00:33:18,900 --> 00:33:23,100
Until I've found love.

321
00:33:24,340 --> 00:33:32,340
I've found this woman who made me
realise work isn't the only thing in life.

322
00:33:33,340 --> 00:33:35,380
The woman who teaches me happiness.

323
00:33:38,900 --> 00:33:43,100
That woman is Chonlalda.

324
00:34:00,780 --> 00:34:02,740
Hello, everyone.

325
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:07,700
I, too, never thought I'd get to
marry a walking robot like her

326
00:34:07,940 --> 00:34:11,380
who only focuses on work, work, and work.

327
00:34:12,580 --> 00:34:16,380
But then, here I am today.

328
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:19,900
From now on, if we
ever fight over anything,

329
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:22,330
I'll never forget this day.

330
00:34:23,330 --> 00:34:25,000
No matter how long time passes,

331
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:27,659
I promise to care for her,

332
00:34:28,199 --> 00:34:29,530
be honest and loyal to her,

333
00:34:30,199 --> 00:34:33,260
for the rest of my life.

334
00:34:48,020 --> 00:34:56,020
