367
00:39:15,300 --> 00:39:16,956
Don't be shy.

368
00:39:16,980 --> 00:39:19,676
Muster up and quickly come forward
if you want to get married this year.

369
00:39:19,700 --> 00:39:24,956
Come on, girls. Our bride is dying to
