370
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:25,980
Go ahead, Miss Nuch.

371
00:39:26,500 --> 00:39:27,500
That's right.

372
00:39:27,530 --> 00:39:31,940
And I'm telling you, this bouquet is very
special-not only because it's beautiful,

373
00:39:32,130 --> 00:39:34,780
but also because it's our bride's love trap.

374
00:39:34,930 --> 00:39:38,460
Whoever gets this bouquet will
definitely get to tie the knot soon.

375
00:39:39,730 --> 00:39:41,180
